<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fy kl ywm bạqḍyh mʿạk ʿynk ʿlyạ mn smạk
 hkẖạf mn ạ̹yh dạ ạ̹nt ạlạ̉mạn ạ̹ydk tḥmyny fy ạ̉y mkạn
 klmtk trsm ṭryq rwḥk ykwn ạ̉fḍl ṣdyq
 wʿwdk tḍmlny ạlḥyạẗ wạ̹n ywm wqʿt fyk ạlnjạẗ
 ạlqrạr- hạrnm lyk ʿsẖạn bḥbk hạrnm lyk hạfrḥ qlbk
 hạrnm lyk mkẖtạr ạ̉ʿysẖlk hạrnm lyk ạ̉nạ kly lyk
 2- ṭwl ạlṭryq mạsk fy wʿdk ạ̹ydy fy ạ̹ydyk dạ ạ̉nạ ạbnk
 ạ̉jry ʿlyk wạ̉sẖbʿ bḥbk ạ̉ftḥ ʿnyạ ạ̉sẖwf qlbk
 nʿmtk tdyny qwẗ tsẖfy kl ạljrwḥ mn jwh
 wḥbk yṭrd kl kẖwf yfyḍ jwạyạ lạ̉lwf</lyrics>
